2022-23 (33G/26S): Averaged 7.2 points, 5.9 rebounds, 0.5 assists, 1.1 steals, and 0.5 blocks...42.6 FG%, 28.6 3ptFG%, 63.7 FT%...posted eight 10+ scoring games, five 10+ rebound games, and four double-doubles...posted first career double-double with career-high 17 points and 10 rebounds along with career-high tying three steals and career-high three blocks vs. Florida A&M (1/23)...scored 13 points with career-high 14 rebounds at Southern (1/30)...tallied 14 points with 12 rebounds vs. Miss. Valley (2/4).

Previous School (Northeast Mississippi Community College) 2021 -2022 - Started in all 29 games. Shot 144-324 (44.4), overall 60-of 92 from the free throw line, 327 total rebounds and 11.3 rebounds per game. Tailed career high 24 points against Copiah-Lincoln Community College (1/20).

Previous School (Northeast Mississippi Community College) 2020 - 2021: Appeared in 19 games and made 12 starts. Shot 63-of-131 (48.1) overall, 38-57 from free throw line. Scored 22 points in the win against Delgado Community College (4/6). Tailed 15 points, 16 rebounds, one assists, and one block Northwest Mississippi Community College (2/25).
